<![CDATA[<p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" id="docs-internal-guid-9090228d-5536-61dc-2a5e-c3ce9f822bac"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Congratulations! Following your assessment we are delighted to provisionally offer you a role with us this summer as a {!Job_Application__c.Role_to_assess_for__c}.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">This offer is conditional upon your completion of the following:</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">DBS certificate</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">All seasonal staff working on the NCS programme must have an ‘Enhanced DBS certificate with Children's Barred List check’ dated from </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">1 January 2015</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">. This is a legal requirement, and you won’t be offered any work dates without one.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">If you don’t already have a valid DBS certificate </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionspostoffer.pdf">click here for instructions on how to apply for one</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">. Please note, you’ll need up to 4 forms of ID to hand to do your application. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">DBS applications can sometimes take up to 6 weeks to process - </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">make sure you start your application as soon as possible!</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">If you already have an existing DBS certificate dated from 1 January 2015 and you didn’t upload it to your application form, please upload a scanned or photographed copy to the Essential Information page now!</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Essential Information </font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Each section of the Essential Information page should be completed before you start your role. This includes:</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin