 none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">bank details </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">(from April)</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Filling out our </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">health, safeguarding &amp; inclusion</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> form</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Providing details for your </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">emergency contact</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Checking your </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">DBS status</span></font></p></li></ul><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">This offer is conditional upon </span><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">availability and </span><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">your completion of the following:</span><br></div><div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></div><div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>Availability and Training</b></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">You'll now also have access to the 'Choosing when I can work' and 'Dates when I can't work' pages. Here, you'll be able to choose which work dates you'd like to be considered for, and indicate days when you won't be available to work. </span></font><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><font color="#000000">The sooner you submit this information, the sooner we </font><font>may be</font><font color="#000000"> able to provisionally allocate you to a work placement! </font><font>Please note that in some instances your availability may not match the placements that we still have available and we may initially offer you a place on our reserve list. </font></span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;">** <b>Please note: If you've been offered the Learning and Behaviour Mentor role, you won't need to fill in your availability online. You can discuss this directly with your Inclusion Staffing Associate.**</b></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The 'Booking Training' page is also now open - here, you'll find a choice of dates to choose from for your training sessions. This training is compulsory, and we can't let you work on the programme without it. Our training sessions fill up fast - login and book your training as soon as possible to secure your place!&nbsp;</font></span></div><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">What else?</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38;">Depending upon your role, you’ll need to attend up to 3 days of unpaid compulsory training for your role. Our training dates will take place from May until July, and you’ll be able to pick your dates from late April.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">We’ll call you in the coming weeks to discuss your availability and talk through any questions you might have about your role. In the meantime, if you have any urgent questions, please contact me using the details below, or check through our </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Congratulations again, and best wishes,</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; 